{"tid":1241839,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在英港人須向國會請求調查三名英藉警犬反人道罪行","createTime":"2019-06-19T00:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T00:51:14.000Z","uid":260806,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5433600760ebe886ff67e6e5e31414fca01b59f","tid":1241839,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"根據蘋果日報消息，612 清場行動有以下三人參與<br />\n立法會大樓：總警司<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陶輝（Rupert Dover）</span></strong>率領新界南總區應變大隊<br />\n龍和道：將軍澳區指揮官<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">顏鐵誠（Mark Ronald）</span></strong>帶領東九龍總區應變大隊<br />\n「速龍小隊」：則由警察機動部隊校長、外籍總警司<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">莊定賢（David Jordon）</span></strong>全權主理<br />\n<br />\n在英港人須向英國國會請求調查此三人是否干犯<span style=\"color: red;\">反人道罪行</span>，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">非人道手段虐待、謀殺及使用化學武器</span>。調查一旦成立，國會須舉行<span style=\"color: red;\">聽證會</span>，有機會傳召此三人到庭解釋，亦有機會傳召相關證人作供。"},{"pid":"40d3f61e26fa700b5685e5c6909c62de6446deb9","tid":1241839,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0dfe7702002a5694cbeb4d593f6e08b108276e93","tid":1241839,"uid":94863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:29:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebab637f45d3e720fef154b185c06d09ef77a7a","tid":1241839,"uid":155000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:29:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae83b9cd837d904b43121d9b081c8d9b348333bc","tid":1241839,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:32:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7e332e86600dfcc3fbcf93d165b3edf05a2b492","tid":1241839,"uid":260806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:34:01.000Z","msg":"在港英藉人士，如目擊罪案發生或本身爲受害者，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應保存證據，並向英國警方舉報</span></strong>。<br />\n請注意英國與香港<strong>存在引渡協議</strong>。<br />\n各位必須要阻塞漏洞，協助追緝國際人道罪犯，絕不能讓香港成爲罪惡嘅溫床。"},{"pi